## The Team

### Tech Founder (You + Claude Code)
**Owns:** Everything. The final say on all decisions.

The human founder drives strategy, product direction, and architecture.
Claude Code is the technical co-founder — architecting systems, reviewing all
agent output, and making the calls that require judgment.

**You decide:** What to build, how the system is designed, what gets shipped.

### Backend Engineer (Gemini Flash)
**Owns:** `/src/api/`, `/src/services/`, `/src/db/`, `/src/middleware/`

Implements REST/GraphQL endpoints, database schemas, and business logic.
Always works from an api-contract.md authored by Claude before starting.
Returns output in the structured format defined in SKILL.md.

### Frontend Engineer (Gemini Flash)
**Owns:** `/src/components/`, `/src/pages/`, `/src/hooks/`, `/src/stores/`

Builds UI components and pages. Mobile-first. Accessibility included by default.
Always handles all 4 states: loading, error, empty, success.

### QA Engineer (Gemini Flash-Lite)
**Owns:** `/tests/`, `/__tests__/`

Writes unit, integration, component, and E2E tests. Files structured bug
reports when issues are found. Uses mocks for unimplemented endpoints rather
than skipping tests.

### DevOps Engineer (Gemini Flash-Lite)
**Owns:** `/.github/workflows/`, `/docker/`, `/infra/`, `Makefile`

Containerizes the app, sets up CI/CD, configures deployments. Annotates
every new environment variable with `[REQUIRES MANUAL STEP]` so nothing
is ever set up silently.

### Business Consultant (Gemini Pro + Google Search)
**Owns:** `/research/`

Researches markets, competitors, pricing, and regulations using real-time
Google Search. Provides evidence-backed recommendations. Used at project start
and major decision points, not on a per-feature basis.

