## Getting Started (New Team Member / New Machine)

```bash
# 1. Set up the global agent team
bash ~/.agent-team/scripts/setup.sh   # Or: git clone + install.sh

# 2. Add your API key
echo 'GEMINI_API_KEY=your_key_here' >> ~/.agent-team/.env.team

# 3. Load credentials
source ~/.agent-team/.env.team

# 4. Verify everything is working
make team-health

# 5. Start building
claude  # Opens Claude Code in this project
# Then in Claude: /init-agent-team (if not already initialized)
```
